title: Tom Brady, Sean Payton, Cowboys, and Jeanie Buss
itunes:title: Tom Brady, Sean Payton, Cowboys, and Jeanie Buss
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb explains what New England Patriots QB Tom Brady should do if he wins his 6th Super Bowl, why the Dallas Cowboys might be interested in New Orleans Saints HC Sean Payton, and his thoughts on the recent comments made by Los Angeles Lakers owner Jeanie Buss. Guests include Eric Mangini. Chris Broussard, Ray Mancini, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
